Package: OrganoidsToolBox
Type: Package
Title: Toolbox for organoids analyses using drug screening and RNA-sequencing
Description: This package is devoted to analyzing organoids related data. The 
    principal focus is to run analyses on drug screening dataset. However, 
    RNA-sequencing analyses are also included.
Version: 0.0.1
